hh3cFtmManMIB.name: hh3cFtmManMIB
hh3cFtmManMIB.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
hh3cFtmManMIB.description: this MIB will maintain Fabric topology management. The MIB includes unit-id, unit-name and fabric authentication information.

hh3cFtmUnitTable.name: hh3cFtmUnitTable
hh3cFtmUnitTable.description: A table of informations of XRN-Fabric Unit.

hh3cFtmUnitEntry.name: hh3cFtmUnitEntry
hh3cFtmUnitEntry.description: An entry for configuring unit informations of XRN-Fabric.

hh3cFtmIndex.name: hh3cFtmIndex
hh3cFtmIndex.description: The unique index of a unit.

hh3cFtmUnitID.name: hh3cFtmUnitID
hh3cFtmUnitID.description: Identifer of unit in fabric. Its value should be between 1 and the maximum which defines in product specification. An exception is described in description of hh3cFtmNumberMode. In that case, the value of this object remains its original value after set to zero.

hh3cFtmUnitName.name: hh3cFtmUnitName
hh3cFtmUnitName.description: Name of unit in XRN-Fabric. It consists of no more than 64 characters.

hh3cFtmUnitRole.name: hh3cFtmUnitRole
hh3cFtmUnitRole.description: Role of unit in XRN-Fabric. One unit in a XRN-Fabric acts as master role and others act as slave roles

hh3cFtmNumberMode.name: hh3cFtmNumberMode
hh3cFtmNumberMode.description: Numbering Mode of unit in XRN-Fabric. If the unit ID is assigned by the auto numbering algorithm, the numbering mode will be automatic numbering; if the unit ID (hh3cFtmUnitID) is assigned by the user, the numbering mode will be manual numbering; if hh3cFtmUnitID is set to be zero, the numbering mode will become automatic numbering.

hh3cFtmAuthValue.name: hh3cFtmAuthValue
hh3cFtmAuthValue.description: Authentication value of XRN-Fabric Feature. ftm_none mode means no authentication. In simple mode, the value is password of a string of 1 to 16 charactors. While in md5 mode, the value is key of a string within 16 charactors.

hh3cFtmFabricVlanID.name: hh3cFtmFabricVlanID
hh3cFtmFabricVlanID.description: The object is used for get and set the Fabric VlanID. Only is the equipment not in the stacking status, the value can be set.

hh3cFtmFabricType.name: hh3cFtmFabricType
hh3cFtmFabricType.description: Topology type of Fabric. outofStack means this unit is not in stack.

hh3cFtmUnitIDChange.name: hh3cFtmUnitIDChange
hh3cFtmUnitIDChange.description: When unit id changes in fabric, this trap is sent with unit index and its new id .

hh3cFtmUnitNameChange.name: hh3cFtmUnitNameChange
hh3cFtmUnitNameChange.description: When unit name changes in fabric, this trap is sent with unit index and its new name.

hh3cFtmMIBCompliance.name: hh3cFtmMIBCompliance
hh3cFtmMIBCompliance.description: The compliance statement for FTM implementing the MIB.

hh3cFtmConfigGroup.name: hh3cFtmConfigGroup
hh3cFtmConfigGroup.description: The basic collection of objects for sending trap of FTM Management.

hh3cFtmNotificationGroup.name: hh3cFtmNotificationGroup
hh3cFtmNotificationGroup.description: The basic collection of objects for sending trap of FTM Management.
